<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>3</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vancung Siangpahrang hmaizahnak pe u, A sunparnak cu hla in thangthat
 u; Amah cu kan phaw le kan himnak asi, Zungzal hmunmi sunparnak Pathian a
 si.

[V2]
 A thawnnak chim u, A velngeihnak zong, A puan ceunak nih zeizong a
 khuh dih. Vanrang le khuadawm cit in a ra lai i, Vawleicung mi vialte bia
 a ceih hna lai.

[V3]
 Na kan zohkhenhnak holh in chim khawh lo, Thli chungah a khat, ceunak
 chung zongah Tlangcung in a rung i tiva nelrawn tiang, Vanruah le dapti
 in dai tein an sur.

[V4]
 Ngakchia bantukin vawleicung mi nih, Nangmah kan in zumh, na kan hleng
 bal lo, Na velngeihnak cu zungzal in a hmun ko, A kan Sertu, Khamtu le
 kan Hawi na si.</lyrics>
<key>A</key>
<title>SIANGPAHRANG BIA TUAH CH3</title>
</song>